## 8. Target Trial Emulation  
## 8. 目标试验模拟

### English

Target trial emulation is a framework for designing an observational study to resemble the randomized trial that would ideally answer the causal question.

The target trial should specify eligibility criteria, treatment strategies, treatment assignment, time zero, follow-up, outcomes, causal contrast, and analysis plan.

Eligibility should be assessed using information available before or at treatment initiation. Treatment strategies should define initiation, continuation, switching, and discontinuation rules.

Time zero is critical. Eligibility assessment, treatment assignment, and follow-up should begin at the same time to avoid immortal time bias and other timing-related biases.

For comparative effectiveness studies, I prefer a new-user, active-comparator design when feasible. A new-user design allows baseline covariates to be assessed before exposure, while an active comparator reduces confounding by indication.

The analysis may estimate an intention-to-treat-like effect or a per-protocol effect. A per-protocol approach may censor patients after deviation and use inverse probability weighting to address informative censoring.

Target trial emulation does not eliminate confounding, but it improves design clarity and reduces avoidable bias.

### 中文

目标试验模拟是一种观察性研究设计框架，目的是让观察性研究尽可能接近理想的随机对照试验，以回答因果问题。

目标试验应明确入选标准、治疗策略、治疗分配、时间零点、随访期、结局、因果对比和分析计划。

入选标准应使用治疗开始前或治疗开始时可获得的信息进行判断。治疗策略应明确启动、持续、换药和停药规则。

时间零点非常关键。资格评估、治疗分配和随访开始应在同一时点对齐，以避免不死时间偏倚和其他时间相关偏倚。

在比较效果研究中，如条件允许，我优先考虑新使用者、主动对照设计。新使用者设计可以在暴露前评估基线协变量，主动对照则有助于降低适应证混杂。

分析可估计类似意向治疗效应或符合方案效应。符合方案分析中，患者偏离策略后可能被删失，并使用逆概率加权处理信息性删失。

目标试验模拟不能消除所有混杂，但能够提高设计透明度，并减少可避免的偏倚。

