## 21. Chi-Square Test Experience  
## 21. 卡方检验经验

### English

I use chi-square tests to evaluate associations between categorical variables, such as treatment response, adverse-event occurrence, hospitalization, comorbidity prevalence, utilization category, discontinuation, disease status, and demographic group.

I typically use PROC FREQ in SAS. Before interpretation, I assess independence and expected cell counts. If expected counts are small, I use Fisher’s exact test.

A chi-square test indicates association but not magnitude, so I may also report risk differences, risk ratios, odds ratios, or Cramér’s V.

In RWE, statistical significance does not establish causality. Results may reflect confounding, selection, coding practices, or access to care.

### 中文

我使用卡方检验评估分类变量之间的关联，例如治疗反应、不良事件、住院、合并症、医疗利用类别、停药、疾病状态和人口学分组。

在SAS中通常使用PROC FREQ。解释结果前，我会检查观察值独立性和期望频数；如果期望频数过小，则考虑Fisher精确检验。

卡方检验只能说明是否存在关联，不能直接反映效应大小，因此我可能同时报告风险差、风险比、比值比或Cramér’s V。

在RWE研究中，统计学显著并不代表因果关系，结果可能受到混杂、选择、编码行为或医疗可及性影响。

