## 26. Survival Analysis Experience  
## 26. 生存分析经验

### English

I have extensive experience with Kaplan–Meier estimation, log-rank tests, Cox models, median survival, landmark rates, hazard ratios, confidence intervals, censoring, competing risks, and time-dependent variables.

Clinical-trial endpoints include overall survival, progression-free survival, duration of response, event-free survival, time to progression, and time to treatment failure. RWE endpoints may include hospitalization-free survival, time to treatment discontinuation, time to next treatment, readmission, progression, or adverse events.

I carefully define time zero, event definition, event date, censoring date, follow-up, population, data cutoff, treatment switching, and loss to follow-up.

I assess proportional hazards using graphical methods, Schoenfeld residuals, and time interactions. If PH does not hold, I may use stratified Cox models, time-varying effects, restricted mean survival time, or milestone survival.

For competing risks, I may use cumulative incidence, cause-specific hazards, or Fine–Gray models depending on the estimand.

### 中文

我具有丰富的生存分析经验，包括Kaplan-Meier估计、log-rank检验、Cox比例风险模型、中位生存时间、里程碑生存率、风险比、置信区间、删失、竞争风险及时间依赖变量。

临床试验终点包括总生存期、无进展生存期、缓解持续时间、无事件生存期、至进展时间和至治疗失败时间。RWE终点还可包括无住院生存、至治疗终止时间、至下一治疗时间、再入院、疾病进展或不良事件。

我会明确时间零点、事件定义、事件日期、删失日期、随访期、分析人群、数据截止日期、换药和失访。

我使用图形方法、Schoenfeld残差和时间交互项评估比例风险假设。若不满足，可考虑分层Cox、时变效应、限制平均生存时间或里程碑生存分析。

对于竞争风险，根据目标估计量，可使用累积发生函数、原因特异性风险模型或Fine-Gray模型。

