## 29. Bias in RWE Studies  
## 29. RWE研究中的偏倚

### English

Important biases include confounding by indication, selection bias, information bias, misclassification, immortal time bias, prevalent-user bias, time-lag bias, surveillance bias, channeling bias, informative censoring, reverse causation, and residual confounding.

Active-comparator, new-user designs and propensity-score methods can reduce measured confounding.

Aligning eligibility, treatment assignment, and time zero helps prevent immortal time bias. New-user designs reduce prevalent-user bias.

No statistical adjustment can fully rescue a fundamentally biased design, so I prioritize design decisions before modeling.

### 中文

RWE研究中的重要偏倚包括适应证混杂、选择偏倚、信息偏倚、误分类、不死时间偏倚、既往使用者偏倚、时间滞后偏倚、监测偏倚、渠道偏倚、信息性删失、反向因果和残余混杂。

主动对照、新使用者设计及倾向评分方法可降低已测量混杂。

对齐入选条件、治疗分配和时间零点有助于防止不死时间偏倚；新使用者设计有助于降低既往使用者偏倚。

统计调整无法完全挽救存在根本设计缺陷的研究，因此我会优先优化设计，再进行建模。

