## 30. Production Analysis Experience  
## 30. 生产分析经验

### English

I have extensive production-analysis experience in clinical trial and RWE settings where deliverables must meet specifications, timelines, quality standards, and audit requirements.

My workflow includes reviewing the protocol, SAP, specifications, and shells; confirming populations and endpoints; developing production programs; performing log and data checks; generating datasets and outputs; supporting independent validation; investigating discrepancies; documenting resolutions; and delivering approved outputs.

I check errors, warnings, uninitialized variables, invalid conversions, duplicate keys, missingness, population counts, denominators, treatment assignments, event timing, and shell alignment.

When production and validation differ, I compare specifications, datasets, derivations, and model settings rather than assuming either side is correct.

### 中文

我在临床试验和RWE环境中具有丰富的生产分析经验，交付物需要满足预先定义的规格、时间线、质量标准和审计要求。

我的流程包括审阅方案、SAP、数据规格和输出壳表；确认分析人群和终点；开发生产程序；执行日志和数据检查；生成数据集和输出；支持独立验证；调查差异；记录解决过程；并交付批准后的结果。

我会检查错误、警告、未初始化变量、无效转换、重复键、异常缺失、分析人群计数、分母、治疗分组、事件时间及壳表一致性。

当生产和验证结果不一致时，我会比较规格、数据集、派生逻辑和模型设置，而不是默认某一方正确。

