## 32. Healthcare Utilization and Cost Analysis  
## 32. 医疗资源利用与成本分析

### English

I evaluate inpatient admissions, hospital days, emergency visits, outpatient visits, specialist visits, procedures, diagnostics, medications, home care, and rehabilitation.

Cost outcomes may include total, medical, pharmacy, inpatient, outpatient, emergency, disease-related, and all-cause costs.

I define whether outcomes are events, unique days, episodes, or patients with at least one event. For hospitalizations, multiple claims may represent one admission, so I create episode-level logic.

Cost data are often skewed, have outliers, and may contain many zeros. I may report means, medians, interquartile ranges, confidence intervals, and per-patient-per-month values.

Adjusted methods may include GLMs, two-part models, bootstrapping, or transformed regression.

### 中文

我分析住院、住院天数、急诊、门诊、专科就诊、操作、诊断检查、药物、居家护理和康复等医疗资源利用。

成本结局可包括总成本、医疗成本、药房成本、住院成本、门诊成本、急诊成本、疾病相关成本及全因成本。

我会明确结局是按事件数、唯一日期、医疗事件阶段，还是至少发生一次事件的患者数进行统计。对于住院，多个理赔记录可能属于同一次住院，因此需要构建住院事件级算法。

成本数据常右偏、含异常值，并可能有大量零值。我会报告均值、中位数、四分位距、置信区间及每患者每月成本。

调整分析可采用广义线性模型、两部分模型、bootstrap或变换后的回归模型。

