## 33. Treatment Pattern Analysis  
## 33. 治疗模式分析

### English

I evaluate treatment initiation, duration, persistence, adherence, discontinuation, switching, augmentation, combination therapy, dose modification, treatment sequencing, and line of therapy.

Treatment episodes may be defined using dispensing dates, days supplied, administration dates, permissible gaps, and clinical rules.

Persistence measures continued treatment before a gap or discontinuation. Adherence may be measured by MPR or PDC.

Switching requires a clear rule distinguishing replacement from temporary overlap, combination therapy, or data noise.

Oncology line-of-therapy algorithms may use start dates, combination windows, treatment gaps, and addition or removal of agents.

I validate algorithms using clinical input, descriptive summaries, and patient-level review.

### 中文

我分析治疗启动、持续时间、持续性、依从性、停药、换药、加药、联合治疗、剂量调整、治疗顺序和治疗线次。

治疗阶段可根据发药日期、供应天数、给药日期、允许间隔及临床规则定义。

持续性反映患者在治疗中断或停药前持续用药的时间；依从性可使用MPR或PDC衡量。

换药必须有清晰规则，以区分真正替代治疗、短期重叠、联合治疗或数据噪声。

肿瘤治疗线次算法通常结合治疗开始日期、组合窗口、治疗间隔及药物新增或移除规则。

我会结合临床专家意见、描述性汇总和患者级审阅验证算法。

